snippet.title: MAME - LETS TV PLAY Classic - Namco Nostalgia 1 - Mappy, Mappy : Revenge of Nyamco
snippet.description:
Here is information on the Lets TV play Classic 
Namco Nostalgia 1: 

Namco 1 - Mappy
============================
This is the first Namco release with Mappy,
and Xevious Featured
-----------------------
Version : MAME 0.217
game    : Namco Nostalgia 1 - Mappy, Mappy : Revenge of Nyamco
OS      : windows 8.1 /64bit
controller : Sega Saturn Joystick through USB


There is slighty music variations, and some
missing elements.

The Revenge of Nyamco is an exclusive
arkanoid/ breakout clone. That includes
the sprites from the Mappy game.

==========================
Gameplay

Mappy : - 00:14 - 03:40   - 2 levels


Mappy : Revenge of Nyamco - 03:41 - 07:13 - 2 levels
----------------------------
later
-1
